===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-knurl.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===

'''knurl'''

#A [[contorted]] [[knot]] in [[wood]].
#A crossgrained protuberance; a [[nodule]]; a [[boss]] or [[projection]].
#A lined or crossgrained pattern of [[ridges]] or [[indentation]]s rolled or pressed into a part for [[grip]].

===Verb===

'''knurl'''
#To roll or press a pattern of ridges or indentations into a part for grip.